RECIPE TRANSFORMER PROJECT

Group: Monisha Appalaraju, Juliusz Choinski, Sam Elberts, Thomas Saxton
Environment: Python 2.7

DEPENDENCIES:
1. NLTK - Natural Language Toolkit
   pip install -U numpy
   pip install -U pyyaml nltk
2. Beautiful Soup 4
   pip install beautifulsoup4
3. urllib2
   Should be standard Python library
4. flask
   installation instructions: http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/installation/
5. string
   Should be standard Python library

RUNNING WEB INTERFACE
1. From command line:
   $ python web.py
2. Point browser to: http://127.0.0.1:5000/

RUNNING COMMAND LINE INTERFACE:
$ python main.py http://www.allrecipes.com/SPECIFIC_RECIPE_URL

PRINTING JSON OUTPUT:
$ python getJSON.py http://www.allrecipes.com/SPECIFIC_RECIPE_URL
